  <section>
    <title></title>

    <para><emphasis role="bold"><guibutton>Access Find Me/Follow
    Me</guibutton></emphasis></para>

    <para>You can access Find Me/Follow Me menu from:</para>

    <orderedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>Your own extension:</para>

        <orderedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Dial the access number.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Enter your passcode and press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>
        </orderedlist>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>Someone else's extension:</para>

        <orderedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Dial the access number.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>*</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Enter your mailbox number and press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Enter your passcode and press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>
        </orderedlist>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>An external phone:</para>

        <orderedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Dial the access number.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>*</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Enter your mailbox number and press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Enter your passcode and press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>#</guilabel></emphasis>.</para>
          </listitem>
        </orderedlist>

        <para>When dialing from an external number, if that number is one of
        your access numbers then you only have to enter your passcode. If the
        person is calling them from a phone that isn't registered as someone's
        access number, it will prompt them to enter their mailbox
        number.</para>
      </listitem>
    </orderedlist>

    <para><emphasis role="bold"><guibutton>Find Me/Follow Me
    Menu</guibutton></emphasis></para>

    <para>This menu is accessed upon entering your mailbox. You will hear your
    Find Me/Follow Me status.</para>

    <para>At this time, you have 2 options:</para>

    <orderedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>You can activate or deactivate based on your current Find
        Me/Follow Me status.</para>

        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>When activate, the expiration time will be 24 hour from the
            activation time.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>When deactivate, the configuration will expire
            immediately.</para>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>

      <listitem>
        <para>You can edit your number(s). The following options are
        available:</para>

        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis
            role="bold"><guilabel>1</guilabel></emphasis> to enable the
            number.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis><guilabel>2</guilabel></emphasis> to disable
            the number.</para>
          </listitem>

          <listitem>
            <para>Press <emphasis><guilabel>3</guilabel></emphasis> to delete
            the number.</para>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>
    </orderedlist>

    <para><emphasis role="bold"><guibutton>For More
    Information</guibutton></emphasis></para>

    <para>See the Listen User's Guide for additional information and advanced
    features.</para>
  </section>
